Sentencas: Tubular cone-shaped Ni-based anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs), with yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte and La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 (LSM) cathode, were investigated with Fe catalyst-loaded activated carbon directly filled in as fuel.
Titulo: Direct carbon solid oxide Fuel Cell-a potential high performance battery

Sentencas: Three identical single cells were operated at different current and it turned out that larger current resulted in shorter operation life and smaller carbon utilization.
Titulo: Direct carbon solid oxide Fuel Cell-a potential high performance battery

Sentencas: A 3-cell-stack, with the segmented cone-shaped cells connected in series, was assembled and tested.
Titulo: Direct carbon solid oxide Fuel Cell-a potential high performance battery

Sentencas: A peak power density of 465 mW cm(-2) and a volumetric power density of 710 mW cm(-3) were achieved at 850 degrees C.
Titulo: Direct carbon solid oxide Fuel Cell-a potential high performance battery

Sentencas: The degradation performance was analyzed according to the electrochemical characterization and SEM-EDX measurement.
Titulo: Direct carbon solid oxide Fuel Cell-a potential high performance battery

Sentencas: Based on the experimental results, the potential of developing such direct carbon SOFC into a high performance battery was proposed.
Titulo: Direct carbon solid oxide Fuel Cell-a potential high performance battery
